'''施蒙·奧斯曹夫斯基'''（{{lang-ru|Симо́н Остро́вский}}；{{bd|1981年|2月2日}}）是[[俄裔美国人|俄裔美國]]新聞工作者和紀錄片製作人，著作包括在2014年為[[Vice新聞|VICE新聞]]報導烏克蘭危機，以及2015年的追查烏克蘭境內一名俄軍的《自拍士兵》紀錄片<ref name="vice selfie">{{cite web|url=https://news.vice.com/video/selfie-soldiers-russia-checks-in-to-ukraine|title=Selfie Soldiers: Russia Checks in to Ukraine - VICE News|website=VICE News|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915185134/https://news.vice.com/video/selfie-soldiers-russia-checks-in-to-ukraine|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更曾在2014年4月短暫被親俄武裝分子綁架。目前擔任[[PBS新聞一小時|PBS新聞一小時]]特約記者的奧斯曹夫斯基也是[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]和{{tsl|en|Alfred I. duPont–Columbia University Award|歐福·I·杜邦及哥倫比亞大學獎}}的得主<ref>{{cite web|title=Simon Ostrovsky - Awards|url=http://www.simonostrovsky.com/awards|website=Simon Ostrovsky|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125142657/http://www.simonostrovsky.com/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 事業 ==
奧斯曹夫斯基在2001年起為《{{tsl|en|The Moscow Times|莫斯科時報}}》報導[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]時事，及後轉到[[法新社|法新社]]報導[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]、[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]和[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]的新聞。

2007年，[[維基解密|維基解密]]公開美國領事館的電報，揭露[[烏茲別克|烏茲別克]]政府支持境內的棉業童工問題，觸發全球發起抵制烏國棉產品的運動<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wikileaks.org/cable/2007/11/07TASHKENT2049.html|title=Cable Viewer|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2015-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522035139/https://wikileaks.org/cable/2007/11/07TASHKENT2049.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯曹夫斯基為[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的《[[新聞之夜|新聞之夜]]》獨家調查此事<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/7068096.stm|title=BBC NEWS - Programmes - Newsnight - Child labour and the High Street|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qOS0jdMY?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/7068096.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他發現[[Topshop|Topshop]]、[[沃爾瑪|沃爾瑪]]、[[H&M|H&M]]等跨國衣服零售商的供應鏈都與烏茲別克有關，導致不少西方買家杯葛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204485304576640723023562098|title=Western Buyers Boycott Uzbekistan's Cotton|author=Neena Rai And Grigori Gerenstein|date=2011-10-19|work=WSJ|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2019-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191005113438/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204485304576640723023562098|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年，奧斯曹夫斯基在《新聞之夜》公開俄羅斯境內的朝鮮勞工營問題，提到英國望族韓寶家族擁有並經營一個名為「俄羅斯木材集團」的公司，而該公司透過支付朝鮮政府聘請朝鮮勞工<ref>{{cite news|title=N Koreans labouring in Russia's timber camps|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/8223188.stm|access-date=2015-06-29|work=BBC UK|date=2009-08-26|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020201/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/8223188.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，他與[[Vice傳媒有限公司|Vice傳媒]]創辦人{{tsl|en|Shane Smith (journalist)|誠·史密夫}}重返朝鮮勞工營<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/video/north-korean-labor-camps-full-length|title=North Korean Labor Camps - VICE - United States|work=VICE|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2016-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202054758/http://www.vice.com/video/north-korean-labor-camps-full-length|dead-url=no}}</ref>，二人兩年後為HBO的VICE紀錄片系列合作拍攝一輯關於脫北者的報導<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Nzm2CidMpM|title=Vice on HBO documentary on North Korean defectors|publisher=YouTube|author=Vice News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113175512/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Nzm2CidMpM |archive-date=2015-11-13}}</ref>。

奧斯曹夫斯基多年深入報導朝鮮外勞問題，他曾在英國報章《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》形容數以萬計的朝鮮勞工被送到亞洲各地，平壤政權透過接觸西方企業得以賺錢<ref>{{cite news|title=Profit from its people: North Korea's export shame|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/profit-from-its-people-north-koreas-export-shame-2370220.html|access-date=2015-06-29|work=The Independent|date=2011-10-14|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qP9QJyER?url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/profit-from-its-people-north-koreas-export-shame-2370220.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年，VICE傳媒聘請奧斯曹夫斯基製作第二季的《[[Vice_(電視節目)|VICE]]》，成功帶領節目奪得[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]的「傑出資訊系列節目」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/vice|title=Vice|work=Television Academy|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2014-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029223236/http://www.emmys.com/shows/vice|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年初，奧斯曹夫斯基協助公司開辦「VICE新聞」，並在新節目調查[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2014年索契冬奧]]的貪污指控<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.vice.com/video/why-the-sochi-olympics-are-the-most-expensive-in-history|title=Why the Sochi Olympics are the Most Expensive in History|work=VICE News|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2015-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908001611/https://news.vice.com/video/why-the-sochi-olympics-are-the-most-expensive-in-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯曹夫斯基亦有關注烏克蘭危機，而他拍攝、沒經修飾的《俄羅斯輪盤》影片讓VICE新聞廣受好評，在同業地位躍升<ref>{{cite news|title=Russian Roulette|url=https://news.vice.com/show/russian-roulette|access-date=2015-06-29|work=Vice|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217135450/https://news.vice.com/show/russian-roulette|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/13/vice-news-ukraine_n_4958908.html|title=Vice News Quickly Makes Mark With Ukraine Dispatches|work=The Huffington Post|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301042601/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/13/vice-news-ukraine_n_4958908.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此系列獲得艾美獎兩個提名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.vice.com/article/vice-news-nominated-for-four-emmy-awards|title=VICE News Nominated for Four Emmy Awards - VICE News|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210015833/https://news.vice.com/article/vice-news-nominated-for-four-emmy-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2015年奪得兩個[[威比獎|威比獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.webbyawards.com/winners/2015/online-film-video/general-film-categories/news-politics-series/russian-roulette/|title=Russian Roulette|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602234445/https://www.webbyawards.com/winners/2015/online-film-video/general-film-categories/news-politics-series/russian-roulette/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]邀請奧斯曹夫斯基加入偵查報道團隊，當中包括已經退下火線的記者[[卡爾·伯恩斯坦|卡爾·伯恩斯坦]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cision.com/us/2017/02/simon-ostrovsky-moves-to-cnn/|title=Simon Ostrovsky Moves to CNN - Cision|date=2017-02-09|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2019-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026190335/https://www.cision.com/us/2017/02/simon-ostrovsky-moves-to-cnn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。翌年，奧斯曹夫斯基加入{{tsl|en|Coda Media|高德媒體}}出任偵查報道編輯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://medium.com/coda-story/simon-ostrovsky-joins-coda-story-as-investigations-editor-53cfb76ab296|title=Simon Ostrovsky Joins Coda Story as Investigations Editor|first=Coda|last=Story|date=2018-01-29|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2018-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203064249/https://medium.com/coda-story/simon-ostrovsky-joins-coda-story-as-investigations-editor-53cfb76ab296|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦為[[PBS新聞一小時|PBS新聞一小時]]作貢獻<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/fearing-u-s-rejection-asylum-seekers-flee-to-canada|title=Fearing U.S. rejection, asylum seekers flee to Canada|website=PBS NewsHour|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129150801/https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/fearing-u-s-rejection-asylum-seekers-flee-to-canada|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 綁架 ===
2014年4月21日，當時正製作「俄羅斯輪盤」的奧斯曹夫斯基在烏克蘭東部[[斯拉維揚斯克_(烏克蘭)|斯拉維揚斯克]]被親俄武裝分子綁架<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mashable.com/2014/04/22/vice-journalist-captured-ukraine/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422193353/http://www.mashable.com/2014/04/22/vice-journalist-captured-ukraine/?utm_cid=mash-com-Tw-main-link|archive-date=2014-04-22|last=Ries|first=Brian|publisher=Mashable, Inc.|title=Vice Journalist Captured in Eastern Ukraine|location=New York City, New York|work=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|date=2014-04-22|access-date=2014-04-22}}</ref>，綁架集團首腦{{tsl|en|Vyacheslav Ponomarev (public figure)|維也切斯拉夫·龐諾馬列夫}}要求以奧斯曹夫斯基換取當局釋放囚犯<ref>{{cite web|title=Kidnapped U.S. Journalist Is 'Bargaining Chip' in Ukraine {{!}} News|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/kidnapped-us-journalist-is-bargaining-chip-in-ukraine/498855.html|access-date=2015-05-31|archive-date=2014-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428100922/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/kidnapped-us-journalist-is-bargaining-chip-in-ukraine/498855.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就在他被綁走前，他正調查有沒有俄羅斯公民涉及烏東的親俄武裝組織，而分離分子在衝突初期極其隱瞞此問題。奧斯曹夫斯基亦曾經出席多場龐諾馬列夫的記者會，會上龐諾馬列夫曾經威脅記者<ref>{{cite web|title=Simon Ostrovsky on His Kidnapping, Detainment, and Release {{!}} VICE News|url=https://news.vice.com/article/simon-ostrovsky-on-his-kidnapping-detainment-and-release|access-date=2015-05-31|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621194123/https://news.vice.com/article/simon-ostrovsky-on-his-kidnapping-detainment-and-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

奧斯曹夫斯基被囚地下室，又被毆打和盤問。鑑於事件備受國際關注，奧斯曹夫斯基在三日後便獲釋<ref>{{cite news|title=Simon Ostrovsky Has Been Released|url=https://news.vice.com/article/simon-ostrovsky-has-been-released|access-date=2014-04-28|work=Vice News|date=2014-04-25|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129021619/https://news.vice.com/article/simon-ostrovsky-has-been-released|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他之後接受加拿大《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》訪問時，形容被綁架的三日是一生中最差的三日<ref>{{cite news|title=How a VICE reporter spent three days as a captive of pro-Russian rebels|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/simon-ostrovsky-how-he-spent-three-days-as-a-captive-of-ukraines-rebels/article22184571/|website=The Globe and Mail|access-date=2015-05-31|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013541/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/simon-ostrovsky-how-he-spent-three-days-as-a-captive-of-ukraines-rebels/article22184571/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 自拍士兵 ===
2015年，奧斯曹夫斯基製作了名為《自拍士兵：俄羅斯入烏克蘭》的紀錄片，調查烏克蘭境內的俄羅斯軍事活動<ref name="vice selfie"/>。奧斯曹夫斯基留意到一名俄羅斯士兵由俄國前往烏克蘭東部戰區的路上，將自拍和其他照片上載上網。於是他親身前赴該輯圖片的拍攝地方，繼而追尋士兵蹤跡。紀錄片最終因其「創新報導」和「傑出運用短片」而在2016年先後獲得{{tsl|en|Alfred I. duPont–Columbia University Award|歐福·I·杜邦及哥倫比亞大學獎}}和{{tsl|en|American Society of Magazine Editors|美國雜誌編輯協會}}獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.journalism.columbia.edu/dupont|title=The Alfred I. duPont-Columbia University Awards - School of Journalism|website=journalism.columbia.edu|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208164337/https://journalism.columbia.edu/dupont|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.magazine.org/asme/ellie-awards-2016-winners-announced|title=ELLIE AWARDS 2016 WINNERS ANNOUNCED - ASME|website=magazine.org|access-date=2018-03-23|archive-date=2016-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115071102/http://www.magazine.org/asme/ellie-awards-2016-winners-announced|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

